217
00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:52.000
It could be practicing English, starting a workout routine,

218
00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:55.000
or even reaching out to someone for help.

219
00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:59.000
And then, just take one small step today.

220
00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:02.000
Not tomorrow, not next week.

221
00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:03.000
Today.

222
00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:06.000
Because action leads to momentum,

223
00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:09.000
and momentum leads to confidence.

224
00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.000
That's right.

225
00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:14.000
Small, consistent actions over time create massive change.

226
00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:17.000
So don't wait for the perfect moment.

227
00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:20.000
Make today the day you start.

